snippet.title: Christmas Clix - WiiWare Christmas Game
snippet.description:
Christmas Clix is a casual family friendly game for the Nintendo Wii™ system.

The goal of Christmas Clix is to quickly remove the colored presents and ornaments that Santa stacks by clicking on the same colored presents.
